paths: Obvious exits: north, east, west, out
description: A series of tunnels branch off from this larger cavern, leading to numerous shops.  The smooth rock walls have been coated with a reflective metallic paint, augmenting the illumination provided by a few luminescent toadstools.  Occasionally, a dwarven janitor passes through, sweeping the floors and humming to himself.
title: [Furniture Foyer]
